=== Noun ===
{{en-noun-reg}}
# A metal [[rod]], generally of [[wrought iron]], for adjusting the burning [[log]]s or [[coals]] in a [[fire]]; a [[firestick]].
# One who [[poke]]s.
# A [[card game]] involving concealed hands, [[bet]]ting on those hands, and (often) [[bluff]]ing.

